    <item>
      <title>Episode 1: Introduction to Lightning Network</title>
      <description>In this inaugural episode, we explore the basics of the Lightning Network - Bitcoin's layer 2 scaling solution that enables instant, low-fee payments. We discuss how Lightning works, why it's important for Bitcoin adoption, and how it's revolutionizing the way we think about digital payments. Plus, we'll show you how podcasters can monetize their content using Lightning payments embedded directly in RSS feeds.</description>
