    <item>
      <title>Episode 2: Lightning Addresses and Value-for-Value Podcasting</title>
      <description>This episode dives deep into Lightning addresses - the email-like identifiers that make Bitcoin payments as easy as sending an email. We explore how podcasters are using Lightning addresses and value blocks in their RSS feeds to create sustainable revenue streams. Learn how to set up your own Lightning address and start accepting Bitcoin payments for your content.</description>
